The fact that it's only 700MB doesn't mean it's not a BRRip. It only means loss of quality due to less bitrate. Of course, it's always a very bad idea to choose 1280x712 when squeezing it into 700MB. This usually gets you a lot of artefacts and blurry crap. It's better to choose 480p for such small filesize.

I dont know why, but I just got an email from my ISP stating that because I downloaded this, I got a copyright infringement notice sent to them. I guess I will only be downloading from trusted uploaders from here on out, and definitely not "Anonymous". Watch yourselves.
